          </name>
        </author>
        
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2022/"/>
        <id>https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2022/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2022/">&lt;p&gt;I hadn&#x27;t planned to do Christmas cards again this year, with the launch of my new app I&#x27;ve had little time for anything else. Anyway, I threw together this card rather hastily after snapping a fun photo of Elphie hanging out of hed bed upside down. Once the cards had been delivered it became clear that the graphic was a little confusing with my mums first reaction was to turn the card upside down!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Elphie&quot; title=&quot;Elphie&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;card1.01dda6c98267ede8.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;card1.3ca2f256374959af.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;card1.01dda6c98267ede8.webp 1024w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;card1.b68a00c3227af5cb.webp 2048w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I added a large gold craft gem to the three yellow lights on the card to add a little sparkle. Neil came up with a lovely poem for the inside of the cards.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;card2&quot; title=&quot;card2&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;card2.cad42f7f9a4971ed.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;card2.4e81a9572d8b1009.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;card2.cad42f7f9a4971ed.webp 1024w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This year we supported: &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.samaritans.org&#x2F;&quot;&gt;The Samaritans&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
