        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2020/"/>
        <id>https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2020/</id>
        
        <content type="html" xml:base="https://www.jimmyff.co.uk/gallery/homemade-christmas-cards-2020/">&lt;p&gt;One November Saturday morning I did this Santa drawing with the idea to make our first ever homemade Christmas Cards!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Santa&quot; title=&quot;Santa&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;santa.c4244d26c345b9cc.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;santa.cb65521daadd95b5.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;santa.c4244d26c345b9cc.webp 1024w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;santa.e7e97a2386bcc76f.webp 2048w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Neil came up with a poem for the inside of the cards.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Poem&quot; title=&quot;Poem&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;poem.e9660d076e010868.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;poem.36d4e523ee6104b9.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;poem.e9660d076e010868.webp 1024w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The hardest bit was I stuck 10 little gem stickers on each of the baubles to give them a bit of sparkle. I ended up sticking over 1000 gems on with tweasers! 😅&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;




&lt;img alt=&quot;Cards&quot; title=&quot;Cards&quot; src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;cards.496da39cabe782f2.webp&quot; srcset=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;cards.7dff2f7f856fb0c9.webp 512w, https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.jimmyff.co.uk&#x2F;processed_images&#x2F;cards.496da39cabe782f2.webp 1024w&quot; class=&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We chose to support two very deserving charities: &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mermaidsuk.org.uk&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Mermaids&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; &amp;amp; &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.ukblackpride.org.uk&#x2F;&quot;&gt;UK black pride&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</content>
        
